summary: American Express shows steady growth from travel spending and new products, even as rising costs and credit risks temper upside.

headline: Agoda Shares Where to Travel Each Month in 2026 Across Asia
summary: Digital travel platform Agoda today released a month-by-month guide to help travelers plan their 2026 journeys across Asia. From heritage cities to island breaks, the list highlights destinations and unique cultural festivities that align with seasonal weather and local calendars, offering a curated itinerary of the best destinations for each month of the year.
